2664	  Let \(M\) be a sheaf of modules on \(\Spec R\) and \(f \in R\). Then every element of the submonoid
2665	  \(\mathrm{powers}\,f = \{1, f, f^2, \dots\}\) acts invertibly on the sections \(\Gamma(M, D(f))\):
